HEADWORD: Wrongheaded
<hw>Wrong"head`ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Wrong in opinion or
principle; having a perverse understanding; perverse.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Wrong"head`ed*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Wrong"head`ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>
